&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;15+ years of sales experience (preferably within SaaS) and&amp;nbsp;5+ years of management experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Understanding of our technical and competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
