&lt;li&gt;Conduct thorough analysis to tier and prioritize accounts in large volumes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertly position Figma and engage cross-functional partners where necessary to drive deals forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage opportunities to advance relationships through in-person meetings and networking opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
