&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end product marketing efforts for Figma&#39;s billing, pricing, and monetization initiatives—including external communications, messaging, and launch strategy for plan updates and new offerings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft clear, concise customer communications that help admins and buyers navigate complex changes&lt;/li&gt;
