&lt;li&gt;Equip Sales with the resources they need to position Figma’s Enterprise capabilities with confidence, so they can grow and win accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the broader marketing team on integrated campaigns spanning onboarding, activation, and retention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
