&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to overall strategy and decision-making about product direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help deliver clear storytelling around customer needs and business opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with product management, engineering, and design peers&lt;/li&gt;
