&lt;li&gt;Design and ship high-quality features and product improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a mentor and provide thoughtful feedback to your peers (and benefit from strong personal and professional mentorship opportunities yourself!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
