&lt;p&gt;This role offers the opportunity to shape how leadership, performance culture, and talent strategy evolve as Figma’s Product Engineering and Data organizations continue to grow and mature.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time role that can be based in one of our US hubs or remotely within the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What you’ll do at Figma:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Product Engineering + Data leadership teams as a trusted advisor, providing strategic guidance on leadership effectiveness, organizational design, and talent strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support continued scaling of the Product Engineering &amp;amp; Data organizations by evolving team structures, roles, and operating models in line with boarder Engineering organizational growth and productivity goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach senior leaders to strengthen leadership capability, team effectiveness, and performance in a high-growth, fast-changing environment&lt;/li&gt;
