&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Own the customer IT and Security relationship during the deal cycle by addressing security questionnaires, RFIs, RFPs, identity and enterprise questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Strengthen Figma&#39;s security reputation by understanding customer concerns about data access and working with product and legal teams to resolve findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Design and scale technical sales efforts, facilitating conversations and connections between our customers, sales and product teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Create thoughtful content to delight customers and internal partners surrounding the Figma platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Collaborate with amazing Figmates to hone your craft and execute daily.&amp;nbsp; We are looking for phenomenal life-long learners who can operate with autonomy and own the market.&lt;/li&gt;
