&lt;li&gt;Foster long-term relationships with partners by creating mutual success plans - including documenting wins and monitoring defined KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate opportunities to mature and streamline our relationships with resellers in context of Figma&#39;s existing sales model&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate our wider partner ecosystem on Figma’s products, services, and capabilities in tandem with the partner enablement team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
