&lt;li&gt;In-house experience at a high-growth B2B or PLG (Product-Led Growth) SaaS company is preferred, where you have directly owned paid marketing strategy and budget rather than managing client accounts in an agency setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in PLG organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
