&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and drive the go-to market strategy for Federal &amp;amp; State/Local sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively inform internal stakeholders on progress, roadblocks, and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage, cultivate, and grow relationships with influential contacts at various Federal departments and agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate internally with sales, engineering, design, product, marketing, and legal — leveraging the expertise and value-add of each team in the deal-closing process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and analyze key performance metrics, including accurate forecasting, pipeline generation, win rate, and deal sizes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire, develop, and coach Account Executives selling into the Federal market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;We&#39;d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/h4&gt;
