&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years’ experience working in a support or community environment for a technical SaaS product, with good technical capability and written communication skills, with the ability to turn complex ideas into easily understood concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;shll1d&quot; data-start=&quot;48&quot; data-end=&quot;103&quot;&gt;Demonstrate a bias toward action and responsiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;9wr7hs&quot; data-start=&quot;104&quot; data-end=&quot;177&quot;&gt;Maintain high attention to detail while prioritizing tasks by urgency&lt;/li&gt;
